text: Andrew Kishino (born March 20, 1970) is a Canadian voice actor with recent roles including Janja on The Lion Guard and Saw Gerrera on Star Wars: The Clone Wars. ==Personal life== He married to voice actress Vanessa Marshall in 2001 and broke up in 2007. ==Other websites== * Category:1970s births Category:Living people Category:American voice actors
title: Andrew Kishino
